name: Chronoplot
body:
A simple timeline maker written in Python.  Currently only exports to ASCII, but will be extended in the future to support different export methods, such as image export (maybe).

## Links

- [Source Code (Github)](https://github.com/darkfeline/chronoplot)
- [PyPi](https://pypi.python.org/pypi/chronoplot/0.1.0)
